<div class="title">Smooth Fun Trip</div>
<div class="substance">Mushrooms & 2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Phoenix&Exact=1">Phoenix</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Phoenix. "Smooth Fun Trip: An Experience with Mushrooms & 2C-I (exp38326)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 26, 2008. erowid.org/exp/38326</div>

<br/>



